at interfaces despite the unconventional\norder parameters, which we attribute to the near degeneracy of the two d-wave\nsolutions and their mixing at a general interface.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 27 Oct 2008 18:12:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 15 Jan 2009 17:52:05 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 26 Jan 2009 22:38:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-11-18"}
