iner trees when the diameter bound is 2k; when the diameter bound is\nincreased from 2k to 2k+1, the minimum Steiner tree weight is reduced by a\nfactor of 2^{1/(2^k-1)}.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 27 Oct 2008 19:15:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 5 May 2011 13:55:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-06-08"}
